{"tid":1804201,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［回帶] 2001年除夕倒數警民互摑警指市民說「HappyNewYear」","createTime":"2019-12-30T22:51:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T03:56:31.000Z","uid":54568,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"681f7bbfd76d279704455eb9e51efc8f1fa7e32e","tid":1804201,"uid":54568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T22:51:00.000Z","msg":"而早在2001年除夕，亦有電視台拍攝到警方在控制場面期間，一名「藍帽子」警員與一名少年互相掌摑，惹來警方濫權疑雲，其後警方強調，少年只是輕拍警員面部說「HappyNewYear」（新年快樂），而警員亦只是用手「㩒住」青年。事後青年到警監會（現為監警會）投訴，然而雖然電視台拍下當時情況，但由於畫面陰暗無聲加上無目擊證人，最終投訴未能成立。<br />\n<br />\n2001年的除夕夜，近1.5萬名市民聚集在尖沙嘴文化中心對開，在踏入2002年的一剎那，一批情緒高漲的青年開始互相推撞，更邊叫囂邊拋擲螢光棒，警方見狀便開始廣播，呼籲市民盡快離開。期間有人高舉花盆擲向地上，市民紛紛跟隨，近2,000個盆栽應聲打碎。<br />\n<br />\n一名「藍帽子」警員隨即步入人群中勸喻青年離開，從無綫電視拍攝的片段可見，有人懷疑態度囂張，與警員推撞，而背向鏡頭的警員則兩度掌摑面向鏡頭、瘦身材的金髮少年。在旁群眾一度起哄，至最後在警員勸喻下離去。<br />\n<br />\n事件傳出後隨即惹來社會各界對警方掌摑市民的濫權疑雲，警方於2002年1月1日回應指，並未收到任何市民被警員不禮貌的投訴，而時任西九龍總區副指揮官古樹鴻則於1月2日的記者會指，並無警務人員被掌摑，只是有青年「用手輕拍警員面頰，並向警員說『OK!OK!HappyNewYear!』（好！好！新年快樂！）」而該名警員亦只是用手「㩒住」青年，以免他在地上拾起螢光棒投擲。<br />\n<br />\n互摑的主角、14歲少年練志偉於1月4日露面，指事件與警方作說的有所出入，強調當日並無掌摑警員，亦無向警員講「HappyNewYear」，只是在被問及「貴庾？」時回答「我大過你」，練志偉在母親陪同下，向投訴警察課投訴警方當晚的處理手法。<br />\n<br />\n事後練志偉被傳媒追訪顯得身心俱疲，1月8日他再接受傳媒訪問時坦言，已對事件感到後悔，並於指當晚先有警員對他「爆粗」說「我&times;你老母」，他便以粗口回應，又重申當日與警員動粗的行為是「佢郁我先，我先至還拖」。對於為了逃避追訪而需要向學校請假一星期，練志偉亦指「淨係想返學」。<br />\n<br />\n警方投訴警察課隨即對此展開調查，直至同年9月3日完成調查工作，投訴警察課指，練智偉的證供並不可信，故有關警員毆打他的投訴並不成立。對於古樹鴻被指以「HappyNewYear」以圖淡化衝突，調查結果指古樹鴻只是將下屬的電話報告向記者轉述，認為古樹鴻並無說謊。<br />\n<br />\n警監會（現稱監警會）於同年10月3日通過投訴警察課的調查報告，時任投訴及內部調查科總警司李家超指，由於電視片段畫面陰暗及無聲，警方亦無法尋找目睹事件經過的目擊證人，故將練智偉指被警員毆打的投訴列為「未能證實」；而協助警方進行調查的唇語專家，則未能對練智偉是否對警員說「HappyNewYear」而作出判斷。<br />\n<br />\n走前左18年<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20150101/53262406\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20150101%2F53262406&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJgbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=6b4809f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20150101%2F53262406&h=9ce97d11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20150101/53262406</a>"},{"pid":"7c97d7d6744771a2ef6df2c9fec2b6b5ead987e5","tid":1804201,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T22:53:03.000Z","msg":"<ins>德國聯署</ins><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1. deadline 25/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MHkcG1&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJgbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=33c0b7c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">2. deadline 30/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/369xL99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F369xL99&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJgbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=6836e788\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/369xL99</a></span><br />\n<br />\n3. 暫時最後一個 deadline <span style=\"color: orange;\">1/1 </span> <span style=\"color: red;\">仲要27000人 </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">［附教學］ <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1803675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1803675</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJgbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=1d4673a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>美國聯署</ins> deadline <span style=\"color: orange;\">3/1 </span> <span style=\"color: red;\">仲要6000人 </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/help-congress-act-mass-genocide-uighur-muslims-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhelp-congress-act-mass-genocide-uighur-muslims-china&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJgbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=9e038be8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/help-congress-act-mass-genocide-uighur-muslims-china</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">deadline fighters 請出招</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a546e041d72eed2a87c006c1170925c65ea484f3","tid":1804201,"uid":101328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T23:06:38.000Z","msg":"我仲記得佢叫志偉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b449ddff19a785aa97c3c59af552f6fdc909ffda","tid":1804201,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a546e041d72eed2a87c006c1170925c65ea484f3","tid":1804201,"uid":101328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T23:06:38.000Z","msg":"我仲記得佢叫志偉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T00:53:16.000Z","msg":"練志偉<br />\n<br />\n唔知 佢而家過成點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該30歲<br />\n唔知係咪仲係咁仇警"},{"pid":"d82567ab4d21705689c515bde55983b67cf43049","tid":1804201,"uid":183601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T09:50:30.000Z","msg":"行得好撚前"},{"pid":"60895295c877f20252c02d26f586c6652f77f5c4","tid":1804201,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d82567ab4d21705689c515bde55983b67cf43049",